Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/Giv3n1337/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlink:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Install Plugins:
    
    vim -> :PlugUpdate

Add Plugin:    
    
    1.) vim ~/.vimrc
    2.) add "Plug 'autor/plugin-name'" 
            between plug#begin() and plug#end()
    3.) esc -> :wq
    4.) vim -> :PlugInstall [name... ]
    
Update Plugins:

    vim -> :PlugUpdate [name... ]

Check Status:

    vim -> PlugStatus

Upgrade Plugin Handler:

    vim -> PlugUpgrade


Detailed information regarding vim-plug:
    
    https://github.com/junegunn/vim-plug 
        
